# Weather Emotion Window UI Design Prompt

Design a premium floating weather cognition window for a philosophical knowledge system called "Philosophy OS".

The component is not a normal weather widget.
It is an "Environmental Cognition Interface" that connects real-world weather conditions with philosophical atmosphere.

## Design Style

Style:
- Minimalist philosophical interface
- Modern museum archive aesthetic
- macOS floating window feeling
- Obsidian knowledge system atmosphere
- High-end academic software UI
- Calm, intellectual, immersive

Avoid:
- colorful mobile weather app style
- cartoon icons
- excessive gradients
- futuristic cyberpunk style
- AI-generated glossy UI

---

# Layout

Create a draggable floating window.

Position:
- top-right corner
- floating above the main interface
- can be collapsed into a small weather orb
- expandable into detailed panel

Window shape:

- rounded rectangle
- subtle glassmorphism
- thin border
- soft shadow
- semi-transparent background
- elegant spacing

Size:

Collapsed:
120 × 120 px

Expanded:
360 × 460 px


